ght not to be=\r\n allowed to mix in the least degree in the yoga. The true love for the Divi=\r\nne is a self-giving, free of demand, full of submission and surrender; it m=\r\nakes no claim, imposes no condition, strikes no bargain, indulges in no vio=\r\nlences of jealousy or pride or anger =E2=80=93 for these things are not in =\r\nits\n composition.&quot; Sri Aurobindo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &nbsp; Best r=\r\negards, \n&lt;div style=3D&quot;BACKGROUND-COLOR:transparent;FONT-STYLE:normal;FONT-=\r\nFAMILY:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif;COLOR:rgb(0,0,0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\r\n=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE:13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:arial, helvetica, sans-seri=\r\nf;&quot;&gt;Narasimha&lt;br&gt;--------&lt;br&gt;Astrology &amp; Spirituality Resources: &lt;a rel=\r\n=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot;&gt;ht=\r\ntp://www.vedicastrologer.org/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;BACKGRO=\r\nUND-COLOR:transparent;FONT-STYLE:normal;FONT-FAMILY:arial, helvetica, clean=\r\n, sans-serif;COLOR:rgb(0,0,0);FONT-SIZE:13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE:13p=\r\nx;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;--------&lt;/spa=\r\nn&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/=\r\nspan&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;blockquote style=3D&quot;BORDER-LEFT:rgb(16,16,255) 2px solid=\r\n;&quot;&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:arial, helvetica, sans-serif;FONT-SIZE:10pt;&quot;=\r\n&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:times new roman, new york, times, serif;FONT-SI=\r\nZE:12pt;&quot;&gt;\n&lt;div dir=3D&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=3D&quot;Arial&quot; size=3D&quot;2&quot;&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;=\r\nBORDER-BOTTOM:#ccc 1px solid;BORDER-LEFT:#ccc 1px solid;HEIGHT:0px;FONT-SIZ=\r\nE:0px;BORDER-TOP:#ccc 1px solid;BO