 v=\r\nery complex and various possiblities are there, it is not possible to list =\r\ndown every option. Moreover, even if such a diagnosis\n is correctly done, v=\r\nery few can have the right knowledge to rectify the situation. Many who cla=\r\nim they can do so, are often doing nothing more than an intelligent guess w=\r\nork. Sometimes it will have results, sometimes not. For all these to be ach=\r\nieved, the starting point is a sound mind in a sound body, as the ancient G=\r\nreeks used to say - &lt;span class=3D&quot;yiv255306719st&quot;&gt;Mens sana in corpore san=\r\no.&lt;/span&gt; -Regards &nbsp;Rajarshi \n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;b&gt;\n&lt;div class=\r\n=3D&quot;yiv255306719MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE:16px;&quot; class=3D&quot;yiv2=\r\n55306719Apple-style-span&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;COLOR:rgb(153,153,153);&quot; class=\r\n=3D&quot;yiv255306719Apple-style-span&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT=\r\n-FAMILY:times new roman, new york, times, serif;&quot; class=3D&quot;yiv255306719yui_=\r\n3_2_0_2_134243527249950 yiv255306719yui_3_7_2_19_1362067846619_92&quot;&gt;awaktam =\r\nwyaktimApannam manyantE mAmabuddhayah |&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY=\r\n:Verdana;COLOR:navy;FONT-SIZE:10pt;&quot; class=3D&quot;yiv255306719yui_3_2_0_2_13424=\r\n3506227946 yiv255306719yui_3_2_0_2_134243527249952 yiv255306719yui_3_7_2_17=\r\n_1362045432997_73 yiv255306719yui_3_7_2_19_1362067846619_93&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D=\r\n&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt; \n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;param bhAwamajAnanto mamAwy=\r\nayamanuttamam ||[7:24]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;d=\r\niv&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:Courier New, courier, monaco, monos=\r\npace, sans-serif;FONT-SIZE:12pt;&quot; class